1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 17-A MRSA §1613 is enacted to read:
3 §1613. Judicial discretion
4 1. Term of imprisonment under this Title. Beginning January 1, 2026,
5 notwithstanding any provision of law to the contrary, the court shall exercise judicial
